flowchart TD
  U[You] --> EC2[Launch AWS EC2 Jenkins Host]
  EC2 --> Setup[Install Jenkins Docker Node Terraform Ansible]
  Setup --> JenkinsReady[Jenkins Pipeline Job Configured]

  Git[GitHub Repository] -->|Webhook or Manual Build| Jenkins[Jenkins]
  JenkinsReady --> Jenkins

  subgraph CI[CI Stage]
    Checkout[Checkout Source]
    Validate[Validate Toolchain]
    NpmCI[npm ci]
    LintBuild[Lint and Build]
    DockerBuild[Build Docker Image]
    DockerPush[Push Image to Docker Hub]
    Checkout --> Validate --> NpmCI --> LintBuild --> DockerBuild --> DockerPush
  end

  Jenkins --> CI

  DockerPush --> Scope{DEPLOY_SCOPE}
  Scope --> Dev[dev]
  Scope --> Staging[staging]
  Scope --> Prod[prod]
  Scope --> All[all -> dev staging prod]

  subgraph Infra[Terraform + Inventory]
    TfInit[terraform init]
    TfValidate[terraform validate]
    TfPlan[terraform plan]
    ApplyCheck{APPLY_INFRA=true}
    TfApply[terraform apply]
    OutputRead[Read outputs app_public_ip ssh_user]
    GenInv[Generate hosts.generated.yml]
    TfInit --> TfValidate --> TfPlan --> ApplyCheck
    ApplyCheck -->|yes| TfApply --> OutputRead --> GenInv
    ApplyCheck -->|no| OutputRead
  end

  Dev --> Infra
  Staging --> Infra
  Prod --> ProdGate{Manual Approval for prod}
  ProdGate --> Infra
  All --> Infra

  subgraph Deploy[Ansible Deploy]
    Provision[Run provision.yml]
    RollbackChoice{ROLLBACK_DEPLOY=true}
    DeployNow[Run deploy.yml]
    RollbackNow[Run rollback.yml with ROLLBACK_TAG]
    Provision --> RollbackChoice
    RollbackChoice -->|no| DeployNow
    RollbackChoice -->|yes| RollbackNow
  end

  GenInv --> Deploy
  Deploy --> Health[curl http://app_public_ip:3000/api/health]
  Health --> Done[Deployment Complete]

  subgraph Obs[Observability Prometheus and Grafana]
    ObsStart[Enable monitoring profile services]
    NodeExp[node-exporter]
    Blackbox[blackbox-exporter]
    Prometheus[prometheus]
    Grafana[grafana]
    Dashboards[Dashboards and alerts]

    ObsStart --> NodeExp --> Prometheus
    ObsStart --> Blackbox --> Prometheus
    Prometheus --> Grafana --> Dashboards
  end

  Deploy --> ObsStart
  Blackbox --> ProbeApp[Probe app /api/health]
  ProbeApp --> Health

  Supabase[Supabase URL and Anon Key from Jenkins Credentials] --> DockerBuild
  DockerHub[Docker Hub Registry] --> Deploy
